text.jpText:
ヘーウプッ！！
お嬢誘うならさあ、やっぱ茶！？
text.enText:
Hee-uppp!!! If you're going to invite a young 
lady, come on, it's tea!

text.jpText:
もーね、ガチでフラれまくってんの！
『とりつくね島うまし』だっけ！？
ぜんっぜんノせらんないわけ！
text.enText:
I've been getting so many rejections! I can't 
get over the fact that I can't get into this! 
I just can't get over it!

text.jpText:
ケドさあ……ウチ、お嬢とデートしたい！
アガりたいし、アゲたいっ。
なんかぁ～～……ガチで～～！！
text.enText:
Kedo sae…… uchi, I want to go on a 
date with your daughter! I want to 
get aggravated, and I want to get aggravated. 
I'm kinda～～…… gachi～!

text.jpText:
う～……っしゃあ、負けねー！！
お嬢ラビュり茶、ありそ！？
ミーティンかまそ！
text.enText:
U～…… sha, I won't lose! Ojisaburi tea, 
ariaso! Mee-tin kamaso!
